	Bellucci love     
	Los Angeles, Sept. 3 (PTI): Italian actress Monica Bellucci is all set to play actor Robert DeNiros love interest in Manual of Love 3.      
	It has DeNiro playing a divorced American professor living in Rome. The actors parts will be spoken partially in English and partially in Italian, Variety magazine reported.      
	Producer Aurelio De Laurentiis said that while the first two movies in the franchise have been successful in Europe  making a combined total of $45 million at the Italian box office  he hopes that by casting De Niro, the third movie will reach a wider audience.
                                                                                                                                                      
